{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started to say, how do I get into the Naval Reserve?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I started giving my background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, stop right there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You want to go into the, the intelligence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got the languages, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they sent me and I got an intelligence commission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right, the first thing they did was send me to Norfolk, Virginia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what did they have me doing but following people around?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing to do with German, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, I was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They'd say, well, we suspect so-and-so of having contacts with such-and-such.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now we want to find-- that's FBI stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to do with any of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So finally I got out of there, and I got a-- got 'em to transfer me to Washington, DC, where there were all sorts of things that did concern me and my language effort.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I-- but then I got [? so-- ?] I had to report to work at 6:30 in the morning in the old Navy Munitions building.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's gone now, but it used to be where the Tidal Basin now is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They've torn the goddamn thing down, it was a hideous thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had to make up-- take all the traffic that came in from the European theater and post it on a big old board four by eight feet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would be joined by the-- I was for the Navy, and there was the Army and there's the Air Force and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we-- at-- at 8:00 we would take this down to the director of Naval Intelligence office and we would brief the old man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Wilkinson.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a grand old man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we would be dismissed.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
